Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:14.89,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:15.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:18.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:23.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:26.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.84,0:00:30.59,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.59,0:00:33.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:36.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:40.35,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:45.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:51.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:54.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:00:59.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:02.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:11.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:13.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:15.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:23.79,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs115\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,190.389)}The Fire-Breathing Caterpillar Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:23.79,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(527.167,710.389)}Dokugander
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor, the paths split up\Nhere and meet up further on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take this path, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.91,0:01:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you find any rare insects,\Ndon't keep them to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.43,0:01:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.23,0:02:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor,\Nwatch your step, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is spectacular!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.29,0:02:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What an unusual insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.15,0:02:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A caterpillar like that\Nwould be a major discovery!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,H-H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's take a short break.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The air really is\Nnice in the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But all the dirt and\Ndust is ruining my looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.65,0:03:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You just don't understand women's\Nfeelings, Mr. Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a river over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's sit by the\Nedge for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The barbarians can stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of way is that for the\NRacing Club's first students to act?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure washing their\Nfaces will do much for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:04:02.72,Default Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through the glow of the fireflies
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:07.99,Default Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the snow out the window
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:17.57,Default Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've spent days and months
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:25.06,Default Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reading and reading
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:32.88,Default Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After the passage of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:39.92,Default Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that cedar door opens
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:47.54,Default Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:51.73,Default Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We make our final goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "The Glow of the Fireflies."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The graduation song? Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:17.57,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50\3c&H35342C&\bord3}Motosugi Elementary School\N East Valley Branch
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They all look so sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like\Na graduation to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:04:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care on your way\Nhome, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Goodbye, Teacher!\N- Goodbye! Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care on your way\Nhome, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am... what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you girls come here\Nto look at the waterfall?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we're on a drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine,\Nbut just stay away from the waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who goes to the\Nwaterfall goes missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We all decided to abandon\Nthe village tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you abandoning\Nthe village?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had enough of\Nthis awful place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,People from the village\Nkeep disappearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's all these sightings\Nof a giant caterpillar...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving this village\Nas soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A giant caterpillar?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you people\Neven doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You should get your things packed up\Nsoon, too, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there really a\Ngiant caterpillar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen it myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but the people of the village\Nsay it's as big as a man,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and that it eats people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we go and look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a man about 50 years\Nold, wearing a white hunting jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't. Have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's taking those\Ngirls so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better go looking for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's the girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You left us waiting\Nlong enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.13,0:06:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't our\Nlittle firebrands, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But they really have\Nbeen gone a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I met some girls heading\Nfor the waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So irresponsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get the heck\Noutta this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You people should leave this\Nmountain as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry,\Nbut we're waiting for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to tell you,\Nbut they're not coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The caterpillar monster's eaten\Nthem, I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Caterpillar monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a huge caterpillar\Nstalking the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It eats people!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all working on\Nabandoning the village now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What nonsense...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...\Nlet's head for the waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice and cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You think there could be a\NShocker base in the area?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You think there's really\Na man-eating caterpillar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,\NI certainly hope there isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like the weather's\Nturning strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect time for ghosts...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please.\NIt's just a caterpillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare us like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A third-degree black belt\Nshouldn't startle so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just hate caterpillars...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please.\NIt's just a little bug...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there, dears.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Might I ask what\Nyou're doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We found a caterpillar,\Nthat's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All that fuss over one\Nlittle caterpillar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help not liking them.\NDo you have a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I do beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.69,0:09:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But, my dears...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a man named Tachibana\Nwaiting for you just down the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We totally forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's waiting for you in\Nthe nearby mountain lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mountain lodge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You took so long to return that\Nhe went to the mountain lodge
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,intending to use their\Nphone to call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you show us the\Nway, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be my pleasure to\Nescort such fine ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Koizumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a caterpillar monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll go this way.\NYou go that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did that man head off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He disappeared the moment\Nhe brought us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:10:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you find it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's locked from the outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You've interfered in Shocker's\Nplans for the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider will\Nsurely follow you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we will kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... they got me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now only one remains...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he arrives,\Nyou will all be sent to hell together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:11.15,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(331,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Koizumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the professor's camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ichimonji,\NI know this is his camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yoshioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible Professor Koizumi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,lost his footing and\Nfell from that cliff?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.97,0:12:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be all\Nright by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, Ichimonji Hayato\Nis in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Hold them in\Nthe underground cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you leading\NShocker this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency! Is anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My professor fell\Nfrom the waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please,\Nwon't someone come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but we're the only\Nones left in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to leave the village\Nfast, Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.10,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a large,\Nman-eating caterpillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what that man\Nsaid was true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in there. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider will come to save us.\NI know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do we tell\Nhim where we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as he finds my pipe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:16:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My pipe has a powerful\Ntransmitter installed in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Mr. Tachibana?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll soon be dead,\Nat the hands of Dokugander!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:03.97,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,It's a transmitter...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:06.50,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,If I trace it back,\NI'll find Mr. Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:16.46,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Inside the waterfall, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,0:17:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to execute the hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:18:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll give the Kamen\NRider a real show.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... time to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Hayato...\Nwhy didn't you notice my pipe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You've fallen for my trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Kamen Rider,\NI've prepared quite a show...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.23,0:19:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider...\Nyou can stand there and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... surrender to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this! And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.80,0:21:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.94,0:21:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Dokugander\Nenter a cocoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.77,0:22:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and see us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.23,0:22:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.38,0:22:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be back some time!\NGoodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye! Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.16,0:22:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye! Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.75,0:22:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye! Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.40,0:22:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back soon! Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.11,0:22:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back some time, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.48,0:22:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.57,0:23:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's {\i1}that{\i0} Shocker cocoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.20,0:23:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.87,0:23:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry to hear\Nabout Professor Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take you to the\Nfoot of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.75,0:23:31.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's cyborg, Dokugander,\Nhad transformed into a giant cocoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.70,0:23:36.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What terrible power will that\Ncocoon unleash on Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.79,0:23:40.51,Cont,,0,0,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,480)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.96,0:23:42.71,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.96,0:23:44.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:46.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is Dokugander,\Nwhom he faces in Osaka Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.57,0:23:50.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After his loss to Kamen Rider,\Nhe escaped in a large cocoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.02,0:23:52.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but appears once more in Osaka\Nas an adult poison moth monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.67,0:23:56.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A deathmatch unfolds in Osaka Castle\Nbetween Rider and Dokugander.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:24:00.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "Dokugander,\NBattle at Osaka Castle!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:24:00.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs115\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,720.389)}Dokugander,\NBattle at Osaka Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:10.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:13.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.39,0:24:15.35,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.35,0:24:18.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.89,0:24:20.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.77,0:24:22.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.65,0:24:24.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.44,0:24:25.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.23,0:24:28.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.32,0:24:33.99,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.99,0:24:37.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.58,0:24:41.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.67,0:24:45.42,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Fire-Breathing\NCaterpillar Monster, Dokugander".